# LegalDraft Pro India - Environment Variables

## Required for AI Draft Generation (OpenRouter - OpenAI Compatible)
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-...

## Required for Email Delivery
RESEND_API_KEY=your_resend_api_key_here

## Optional - for Supabase (existing payment flow)
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_url
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key

## Optional - for Razorpay (existing payment flow)
VITE_RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=your_razorpay_key_id
RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=your_razorpay_key_secret

## Notes:
# - RESEND_API_KEY: Use the "LegalDraft Pro Production" key from resend.com
# - DEEPSEEK_API_KEY: Get from https://platform.deepseek.com/
# - For testing with onboarding@resend.dev, recipient must be your Resend account email
# - To send to any email, verify a domain at resend.com/domains
